            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"a1-socket-creation-and-binding-observations\">A1 \u2014 Socket Creation and Binding: Observations</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Throwaway experiments for topic A1. The growing system code lives in <code>../kvstore/server.py</code>. This notebook is for observing kernel/OS behavior.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>BUILD (from curriculum):</strong> Create a Python script that (1) creates a TCP socket, (2) binds it to localhost on a port, (3) prints the FD. Then try binding two sockets to the same port. Then try binding to port 0.</span></span>"
          }
        }
